OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThere will still be a lot of
OL,6,Fcloud around on Saturday with
OL,7,Foutbreaks of light and patchy drizzle
OL,8,Fdeveloping from the south. The best of
OL,9,Fany sunshine likely in the far west of
OL,10,FCarmarthenshire and Pembrokeshire.
OL,11,FFeeling a little milder.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloudy overnight with further
OL,14,Foutbreaks of patch rain and drizzle,
OL,15,Fhowever some heavier bursts are likely
OL,16,Fto develop and move northwards, before
OL,17,Fbecoming more extensive later in the
OL,18,Fnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
